Text: Re field visit of EOTT tanks Cc Campbell PM To Team AndrewsET NRON Team nron Myron cc James R LawrenceET nron Scott NRON William nron Subject field visit of EOTT tanks In the final phase of developing and determining environmental compliance for the EOTT crude oil tanks in the Midland Region I have planned a one day site visit on the following days to visit each team location to finalize the spreadsheet for EOTT crude oil tank environmental compliance Andrews team August am Spraberry team August am Lamesa team August am I would appreciate one member from each team be available at the team office on the assigned day and time to discuss tank history and possibly visit each tank farm within the teams area of responsibility Your patience and assistance in finalizing this information will be greatly appreciated If a conflict arises give me a call at
